    "en": {
      "title": "Viewsonic launches ViewBoard 52 series interactive display with integrated multimedia sound bar",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "ViewSonic, a leading global provider of visual solutions, launches its latest generation of ViewBoard interactive flat panel displays, the ViewBoard 52 series.",
        "The ViewBoard 52 series flat panel displays come in 65 inch, 75 inch and 86 inch options, and operate on Android 9.0 and are compatible with Windows, Mac, Chrome and Linux with full-touch input functionality for all connected devices. The ViewBoard 52 series also features advanced audio capabilities built with a user-centric design to improve classroom and learning experiences.",
        "The ViewBoard 52 is uniquely equipped to support teachers with superior sound integration with a brand-new innovative exterior design with easily accessible enhanced management tools and control systems, such as front facing USB-C inputs for easy connection to additional devices and functional keys and I/O ports in a direct line of sight.",
        "\u201cViewSonic\u2019s rate of growth in the interactive display market has been astounding and staying ahead of the curve. From 2017 to 2020, ViewSonic\u2019s growth rate was up to 16 times above the industry average,\u201d said ViewSonic Presentation Group Director Monica Sun. \u201cThe growth reflects ViewSonic\u2019s dedication in meeting the needs of education applications. The ViewBoard 52 series is a new design, incorporating user-friendly functionalities, together with our myViewBoard visual learning platform, aiming to create more engaging learning and meeting spaces.\u201d",
        "myViewBoard is a visual learning platform that provides a comprehensive suite of applications which operate on the ViewBoard 52 series to deliver advanced communication, collaboration and engagement. ViewBoard Cast delivers the efficiency and productivity of group collaborations where students can easily share screens from their devices through myViewBoard Display, a browser-based wireless presentation tool, without downloading any apps.",
        "ViewSonic has also included a variety of accessories to use together with the ViewBoard 52 series. This includes the ViewBoard Pen Display ID1330 which is a 13.3 inch portable pen, the ViewSonic VB-CAM-002 USB Webcam, the ViewSonic Tribe VB-CAM-201 4k video conferencing camera and the ViewSonic VB-VIS-002, an easy-to-use, plug-and-play USB document camera that is an essential tool for hybrid education setups."
      ],
